  "detailed_description": "<h1>FIND HMUR!</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1343520/extras/b009372be95605a3fb4580f8fe3b1d8f.poster.avif?t=1769713699\" width=1170 height=426 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1343520/extras/b009372be95605a3fb4580f8fe3b1d8f.webm?t=1769713699\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1343520/extras/b009372be95605a3fb4580f8fe3b1d8f.mp4?t=1769713699\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><u>ABOUT THIS GAME</u></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Twenty years after a pandemic, the world is empty and dangerous. Explore the open world, scavenge supplies, craft tools, and build a shelter to survive day after day. Manage hunger, thirst, stamina, health, and radiation as you hunt, farm, mine, and defend yourself from hostile enemies and animals.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1343520/extras/239615333a696b2b1fdc5360e8b76d9d.poster.avif?t=1769713699\" width=550 height=206 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1343520/extras/239615333a696b2b1fdc5360e8b76d9d.webm?t=1769713699\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1343520/extras/239615333a696b2b1fdc5360e8b76d9d.mp4?t=1769713699\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><u>GAME FEATURES:</u></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Character Health, Hunger, Thirst, Energy, Radiation Mechanics</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Driving System</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Building System</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Multiplayer</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Skill System</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Quests</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Level System</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Open World</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Crafting System</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Farming</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Gathering Resources</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enemies</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Mining and refining of ores</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Day and Night Cycle</p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><u>ABOUT THIS GAME</u></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Twenty years after a pandemic, the world is empty and dangerous. Explore the open world, scavenge supplies, craft tools, and build a shelter to survive day after day. Manage hunger, thirst, stamina, health, and radiation as you hunt, farm, mine, and defend yourself from hostile enemies and animals.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1343520/extras/239615333a696b2b1fdc5360e8b76d9d.poster.avif?t=1769713699\" width=550 height=206 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1343520/extras/239615333a696b2b1fdc5360e8b76d9d.webm?t=1769713699\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1343520/extras/239615333a696b2b1fdc5360e8b76d9d.mp4?t=1769713699\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><u>GAME FEATURES:</u></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Character Health, Hunger, Thirst, Energy, Radiation Mechanics</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Driving System</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Building System</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Multiplayer</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Skill System</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Quests</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Level System</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Open World</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Crafting System</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Farming</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Gathering Resources</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enemies</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Mining and refining of ores</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Day and Night Cycle</p></li></ul>",
